<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1437,496,1027]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,965,991]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species resembles 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Toda &amp; Banziger" authorityYear="2020" box="[583,763,965,991]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Phortica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="andreagigoni">
